dct_title_s: Die Eisenbahn-Konzessionen in der asiatischen Türkei im Jahre 1914 nach den Verträgen entworfen von Generalleultnant z.D. Imhoff-Berlin.
dct_description_sm: Ancillary map: Fortsetzung der Hedschasbahn. Scale 1:10,000,000. Shows  completed and projected railways concessions by  country. Ancillary map shows: Hejaz railway In lower left margin: "Leitung: Prof.Paul Langhans." Original map  is filed in the Map/Geospatial Center. A map reproduction is attached to companion volume.
